  "description": "<p><span style='font-size: 14px; font-family: \";'><strong>Application:</strong></span><br></p>\n<p><span style='font-size: 14px; font-family: \";'>2007-2021 Jeep Wrangler JK JL</span></p>\n<p><br><span style='font-size: 14px; font-family: \";'><strong>Features:</strong></span><br><br><span style='font-size: 14px; font-family: \"color:#FF9900;'><em>The adjustable minimum eye to eye length is 8.3in. (210mm). The adjustable maximum eye to eye length is 12.6in. (320mm). The adjustable length is 4.4in. (110mm)</em></span><br><br><span style='font-size: 14px; font-family: \";'>Adjustable Front Sway Bar Quicker Disconnect System 2.5-6in. lift</span><br><span style='font-size: 14px; font-family: \";'>Link is mountable, adjustable and greased</span><br><span style='font-size: 14px; font-family: \";'>Great Improve Off-Road Performance</span><br><span style='font-size: 14px; font-family: \";'>Adjustable Threaded Body to adopt Your Vehicle</span><br><span style='font-size: 14px; font-family: \";'>Replace Fixed mounted version of 2030 and 2034 front sway bar disconnects</span><br><span style='font-size: 14px; font-family: \";'>Easy Lubrication with Convenient Grease Fittings Allow</span><br><span style='font-size: 14px; font-family: \";'>The accessories in the photos are included</span><br><span style='font-size: 14px; font-family: \";'>1 year warranty for any manufacturing defect</span><br><br><span style='font-size: 14px; font-family: \";'><strong>Sway Bar Benefit:</strong></span><br><br><span style='font-size: 14px; font-family: \";'>Helps to stabilize the body of the vehicle relative to the suspension. It is fixed on two chassis guide rails and is connected to the axle housing through the connecting rod at the end of the beam. The spring steel structure of the handlebar makes it work like a torsion bar and resists the body roll when turning.</span></p>",
